    "title": "Wimbo wa Kristo: Asili ya Kimungu ya Kristo",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "wimbo wa kristo: asili ya kimungu ya kristo",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Kifungu katika <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:6-Phil2:11\">Wafilipi 2:6–11</a> mara nyingi huitwa Wimbo wa Kristo. Sehemu hii inaonyesha imani ya Wakristo wa mapema kuhusu Yesu Kristo. Wimbo huo unaonyesha kwamba Wakristo wa mapema waliamini Yesu alikuwepo kabla ya kuzaliwa kwake duniani na kwamba ana asili ya kimungu (tazama pia <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:15-Col1:20\">Wakolosai 1:15–20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:9\">2:9</a>; linganisha <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:1-John1:2\">Yohana 1:1–2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:1-Heb1:3\">Waebrania 1:1–3</a>).</p><p>Wimbo unafundisha kwamba Kristo si nabii wa kibinadamu tu. Alikuwa na Mungu Baba tangu mwanzo. Yeye ndiye ambaye Mungu aliumba ulimwengu kupitia kwake. Kama Mwana wa Mungu, Yesu anashiriki asili ya Mungu mwenyewe.</p><p>Madai haya kuhusu Yesu kuwa wa kiungu yalisababisha mizozo mikubwa kati ya Yesu na viongozi wa kidini wa wakati huo. Walimshtaki Yesu kwa kukufuru (kuzungumza kwa njia inayomdhalilisha Mungu) alipodai kuwa sawa na Mungu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:16-John5:18\">Yohana 5:16–18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:54-John8:59\">8:54–59</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:30-John10:39\">10:30–39</a>).</p><p>Wimbo huo pia unafundisha kwamba Yesu Kristo alikuja duniani kwa unyenyekevu mkubwa. Mungu asiye na mwisho (ambaye ni wa milele na hayuko chini ya wakati) alichukua asili ya kibinadamu katika nafsi ya Yesu Kristo na akaingia katika historia ya binadamu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:7\">Wafilipi 2:7</a>; tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:15\">Wakolosai 1:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:10-John1:14\">Yohana 1:10–14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:14\">Waebrania 2:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:17\">17</a>). Yesu Kristo, Muumba mtukufu wa ulimwengu, alikufa kama dhabihu kwa ajili ya dhambi za wanadamu. Hii ilikuwa ili kupata msamaha na kuwapatanisha wanadamu na Mungu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:8\">Wafilipi 2:8</a>; tazama<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:14-John3:17\">Yohana 3:14–17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:9-Rom5:10\">Warumi 5:9–10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:20\">Wakolosai 1:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:22\">22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:13-Col2:14\">2:13–14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:3\">Waebrania 1:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:9-Heb10:14\">10:9–14</a>). Maandiko yalikuwa yametabiri jambo hili (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:3-Isa53:12\">Isaiah 53:3–12</a>).</p><p>Wimbo huu unasema kwamba Mungu alimfufua Yesu kutoka kwa wafu na kumpa heshima ya juu zaidi mbinguni (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:9\">Wafilipi 2:9</a>). Mungu pia alimpa jina &quot;Bwana&quot; (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:11\">Wafilipi 2:11</a>; linganisha <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:18\">Wakolosai 1:18</a>). Siku moja, viumbe wote walioumbwa watapiga magoti mbele yake na kumtambua kama Bwana wa ulimwengu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:9-Phil2:11\">Wafilipi 2:9–11</a>). Anastahili ibada ambayo ni Mungu pekee anayepaswa kupokea (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev5:8-Rev5:14\">Ufunuo 5:8–14</a>).</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:3-Isa53:12\">Isaya 53:3–12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:1-John1:2\">Yohana 1:1–2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:10-John1:14\">10–14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:14-John3:17\">3:14–17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:9-Rom5:10\">Warumi 5:9–10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:6-Phil2:11\">Wafilipi 2:6–11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:15-Col1:22\">Wakolosai 1:15–22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:9\">2:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:13-Col2:14\">13–14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:1-Heb1:3\">Waebrania 1:1–3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:14\">2:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:17\">17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:9-Heb10:14\">10:9–14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev5:8-Rev5:14\">Ufunuo 5:8–14</a></p>",
